{"tid":1537594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非並唔係無用 但係和理非既抗爭方式係要長時間投入咁去做","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:42.000Z","uid":30791,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b60f8bb5345d54722659051b4d6ec1b3c4c0403e","tid":1537594,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"64年前 美國蒙哥馬利市發生了聯合抵制巴士運動<br />\n蒙哥馬利市幾乎所有黑人拒絕乘坐黑人隔離巴士<br />\n直至 384 日後才取得勝利<br />\n<br />\n有多少人願意從今天起無限期罷搭黨鐵?<br />\n有多少人每個月出糧就轉移資金去外國戶口?<br />\n一個人做 只係微不足道<br />\n但係幾百萬人一齊做日日做無限期做 就有好大威力<br />\n<br />\n大家係香港見到過既只係&quot;一兩日和理非&quot;<br />\n而唔係鐵定心腸 堅持到底 一齊做日日做無限期做既和理非<br />\n所以我明白點解大家否定和理非既抗爭<br />\n因為香港人還沒有抗爭到底的決心和意志<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532109</a>"},{"pid":"25743b4ff78176e74e426a6648869b64d581da6b","tid":1537594,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3144a89880458f9f09c6f04749f3128979494b09","tid":1537594,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年蒙哥馬利市黑人係<br />\n</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以步行、自行車等搭乘方式解決日常所需</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 為了抗爭<br />\n你願意增加自己生活的不便嗎?<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ad1903240ad896f32f616ca581329b42c817b2a","tid":1537594,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說無用</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無用只係因為香港人 包括你 沒有堅持下去</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3f8d70ff9a1a1f9a87561c71fcfa10a702360ddd","tid":1537594,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"唔好嬲1-2 日就算<br />\n諗下佢地點對自己"},{"pid":"d6a39702cdfca096299f04e6825c04d04a29ad0c","tid":1537594,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80510f4c43a3aad9628d8ac96f7fae9f227b2269","tid":1537594,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x